node.text:
Serves 2-4 people 
1 small eggplant
1small zucchini
3 cloves of garlic
½ a bunch of fresh basil , (15g)
1 teaspoon dried oregano
1 teaspoon dried chilli flakes
olive oil
1 tablespoon baby capers
1 tablespoon red wine vinegar
1 x 400 g tin of good quality plum tomatoes
320 g dried wholewheat spaghetti
50 g pecorino/Parmesan or ricotta cheese (for non-vegans) 
extra virgin olive oil

node.text: Hi guys! I realize I never really talk about things that are very personal to me, so I thought in this video I would share a little bit about my modelling journey and my struggle with alcoholism and addiction and how it wasn’t until I decided to accept the help offered to me and do the work on myself that I ended up with a life I never dared to dream of. I hope this video can inspire you to not feel ashamed of asking for help if you are going through something similar, and know that you are not alone, whatever you are going through. All my Love and strength❤️

node.title: A day at a shoot and my modelling story!

node.text:
Unboxing my summer essentials for @laboucherougeparis 

The small collection consists of 5 items: two exclusive lipstick shades Le Nude Elsa and Le Rouge Elsa, the perfect nude and orangey-red, a highlighter, a versatile eyeshadow/contour palette and a mascara, all refillable and housed in upcycled leather cases crafted by French artisans in my favorite colors this season: a pastel lilac and an vibrant lime green. 
 
A portion of proceeds from this collaboration will be going to Every Mother Counts (@everymomcounts), a non-profit dedicated to making pregnancy and childbirth safe for every mother, everywhere.
 
Shop #ELSAHOSKXLABOUCHEROUGE now via the link in my bio. Limited quantity. No restock. #laboucherouge #elsahosk #sustainableluxury

Video by the amazing @kulikulikulik @ruslanpelykh 🔫💚

node.text:
It’s here!! so proud of my makeup collection in partnership with @laboucherougeparis 🌸💞💕

(Avaliable now in limited quantities via the link in bio)

I wanted to share a piece of me, my style and my vision. I wanted this collection to evoke good vibes, to energize you and encourage you to be YOU, have fun with makeup and be kind to the planet. Discover my clean, refillable and microplastic-free collection. Each piece embodies traditional French craftsmanship, elegance, and sustainability proving that taking care of the planet can also be sexy. 
Hope you like it as much as I do! 
 
A portion of proceeds from this collaboration will be going to Every Mother Counts, a non-profit dedicated to making pregnancy and childbirth safe for every mother, everywhere.

Ph: @amberasaly 🌸
Makeup: @leahdarcymakeup 🌸
Hair: @hairbyyuichi 🌸
 
#elsahoskxlaboucherougeparis #laboucherouge #sustainableluxury

For the colors I was inspired by my move to California, all the green plants and exotic flowers fits perfectly with La bouche rouge's use of clean formulas, natural origin ingredients, pigments and the message of natural beauty🌸

node.text:
Hi my Angels💚 introducing my very first sustainable, clean makeup collection in partnership with @laboucherougeparis, available soon.
For my debut collection, I wanted to make the essential makeup items to go with my every day style and making sure each item would be the perfect addition to any summer wardrobe! 
 
Head to the link in bio and sign up to the newsletter to be notified when it’s here. By subscribing to the newsletter, you'll receive an early access to shop the collaboration. #comingsoon #elsahoskxlaboucherougeparis #laboucherouge #sustainableluxury
